&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;University Hospitals Bristol and Weston are looking to recruit to their band 6 team in Bristol (Adults). We are seeking confident, enthusiastic individuals with effective communication and organisational skills, wishing to join a dynamic team. Applicants must have a minimum of three years current Emergency department experience and be proficient in Resus and triage. You should have a strong commitment to patient safety and operational performance.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking confident, enthusiastic individuals with effective communication and organisational skills. You should already be a competent and resilient emergency nurse, who wishes to develop their leadership skills. you should have a strong commitment to patient safety and operational performance. In order to apply we ask that you can evidence 3 years ED or equivalent experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;We look forward to meeting you.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cally Preece cally.preece@uhbw.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
